name: Vision Villa Resort
address: Jl. Pantai Masceti, Medahan, Kec. Blahbatuh, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80581, Indonesia
review 1:
We felt very welcome at Vision Villa. The staff is amasing. We can't give them enough credit for their way of treating us. Very friendly and forthcoming; doing their best to make us feel good.
Our room, Ganesha, #104, was great. We especially, loved the showerfacility. The room was nice and clean, the bed made us sleep like babies. And the ac worked perfect. Being located to a room just beside the great pool, was just another plus. üëç
The hotel garden is really a place where you can lean back and relax.
We had breakfast and dinner at the restaurant twice. And we can only recommend it. Great food, allthough you must think twice before you order breakfast. A "fried egg" is not just a fried egg. It's a meal. üòãüëç.  We recommend you try the Kung Pao Chicken and the Falafel Bowl. If you do want the burger, remember your toothbrush. The charcoal bun is great, but it is rrrrrreally black. üòâ
We recommend Vision Villa to everyone. Singles, couples and families with kids.
A special thank to Triana, Kane and Yuanita who made our stay so so good.
review 2:
We are just amazed. Everything here is just awesome.

Amazing staff which solves your every request with a smile, helps you and advise you with usefull tips on what to do in the neighbourhood, super delicious food. Oh sorry, that is not correct, the food is more than that! I liked everyrhing here. Since I am an vegetarian, this was a paradise for me. And those home mada brownies and chocolate! Unbelievable!

The views in the garden are so calming, the peace and traquility. Nothing less.

And lady in a spa is just perfect. Massages were so calming and she helped me with my back pains.

And staff were more than nice to our daughters.

I more than recommens to stay here, staff will do everything to make your stay unforgetable.
review 3: Luxurious, comfortable, gorgeous place with superkind personel for a good price! The food is a feast for the body and soul. The rooms are spacious and beautiful designed. I will come back next year! A big thanks for a lovely start of my workation!
review 4:
Had an amazing experience at Vision Villa Resort.
The hospitality was simply amazing. The whole ambience is one of the best for retreats, for a calm and serene vacation and for entrepreneurs and business owners to have a space to unfold their business strategy and vision. The amenities are really good. And quite spacious. Very helpful staff who deliver awesome service. Food is simply amazing. Highly recommend that you check it out if you are looking for a resort at Bali.
review 5:
The place is very comfortable, clean. I am very happy with the atmosphere
the food is also delicious
the staff are very friendly, especially Yuanita

name: Genius Caf√© Gianyar
address: Jl. Pantai Masceti, Medahan, Kec. Blahbatuh, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80581, Indonesia
review 1:
Incredible cafe. Nice seating inside, outside and they have an Airconditioned section which is really nice after a hot long ride. The staff are specially friendly and l have to give a big shout out to fabulous NANA that served me through my morning session. Amazing service along with a very welcoming happy smile. It is a really nice cafe to enjoy a coffee, shake, cake or meal. Ib as able to get some much needed research done from their fast WIFI connection and sit in absolute peace.
Highly recommend and the food is so well prepared and you can feel the love. Excellent taste and ingredients. Thank you for an amazing experience and hopefully l can get back sooner than later üôèüèª
review 2: Amazing breakfast choices and beautiful location. We came back 2 times here for lunch and breakfast and everything tastes super delicious. Can definitely recommend the smoothie bowls! Also the stuff is super helpful and friendly. Really a wonderful little oasis!
review 3: We had a really pleasant lunch here. The location, the view, the atmosphere is so beautiful and calming. Super green and just an overall nice look and feel. The service is super friendly and the food was amazing! We had the zinga burger and the falafel bowl and both were super delicious. The coffee was fantastic and Budi the barista was so friendly and gave us lots of recommendations for Bali exploration. Can definitely recommend this place!
review 4: Perfect quit place for work or chill with tasty organic food. I apretiate many gf a vegan options.
review 5: The Foods super delicious, quite place, and their staff so friendly.
